[
    {
        "text": "Researchers have set up a system",
        "start": 0.119,
        "duration": 1.991
    },
    {
        "text": "that lets them see mutations in living cells",
        "start": 2.11,
        "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
        "text": "and follow the cells’ fates.",
        "start": 4.95,
        "duration": 1.659
    },
    {
        "text": "Good, bad, or neutral---",
        "start": 6.609,
        "duration": 1.471
    },
    {
        "text": "spontaneous mutations are not easy to detect",
        "start": 8.08,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "in a living system.",
        "start": 10.64,
        "duration": 1.52
    },
    {
        "text": "But there are important unanswered questions",
        "start": 12.16,
        "duration": 2.469
    },
    {
        "text": "about how mutations are distributed",
        "start": 14.629,
        "duration": 2.131
    },
    {
        "text": "and how common they are.",
        "start": 16.76,
        "duration": 1.75
    },
    {
        "text": "This information makes it possible",
        "start": 18.51,
        "duration": 1.46
    },
    {
        "text": "to use the mutation rate of organisms",
        "start": 19.97,
        "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
        "text": "to look back in time to see when",
        "start": 22.45,
        "duration": 1.81
    },
    {
        "text": "two related species diverged.",
        "start": 24.26,
        "duration": 2.27
    },
    {
        "text": "In this view,",
        "start": 26.53,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "the mother cells are along the top of a micro-fluidic\nchip,",
        "start": 27.53,
        "duration": 3.13
    },
    {
        "text": "so-named because narrow channels",
        "start": 30.66,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "control the liquid’s flow in very specific ways.",
        "start": 32.66,
        "duration": 3.399
    },
    {
        "text": "The offspring bud off and",
        "start": 36.059,
        "duration": 1.691
    },
    {
        "text": "expand into the tiny tubes,",
        "start": 37.75,
        "duration": 2.23
    },
    {
        "text": "each cell pinched off from its progenitor.",
        "start": 39.98,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "Newly made cells",
        "start": 42.42,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "are whisked away by liquid at the bottom of the tube.",
        "start": 43.8,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "Bacteria are red and",
        "start": 46.76,
        "duration": 1.42
    },
    {
        "text": "replication error machinery--markers for mutation-",
        "start": 48.18,
        "duration": 3.379
    },
    {
        "text": "are the yellow dots.",
        "start": 51.559,
        "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
        "text": "Researchers followed cells over 200 generations",
        "start": 53.379,
        "duration": 3.311
    },
    {
        "text": "to look for mutations and",
        "start": 56.69,
        "duration": 1.219
    },
    {
        "text": "the effects those mutations had.",
        "start": 57.909,
        "duration": 1.951
    },
    {
        "text": "They were able to calculate the rate of deadly mutations --",
        "start": 59.86,
        "duration": 2.799
    },
    {
        "text": "at about 1% --",
        "start": 62.659,
        "duration": 1.991
    },
    {
        "text": "much lower than expected.",
        "start": 64.65,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "They also found that mutations occur regularly",
        "start": 66.33,
        "duration": 2.87
    },
    {
        "text": "in individual cells--",
        "start": 69.2,
        "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
        "text": "they all get mutations",
        "start": 71.0,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "at about pretty much the same rate,",
        "start": 72.68,
        "duration": 1.46
    },
    {
        "text": "regardless of stress level--",
        "start": 74.14,
        "duration": 1.89
    },
    {
        "text": "and that mutations are less detrimental",
        "start": 76.03,
        "duration": 2.35
    },
    {
        "text": "to the bacteria than expected.",
        "start": 78.38,
        "duration": 2.01
    },
    {
        "text": "This new technique tracking mutations in single cells",
        "start": 80.39,
        "duration": 2.71
    },
    {
        "text": "could be used in cancer research or",
        "start": 83.1,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "to explore different mutation patterns in\ndifferent tissues.",
        "start": 85.28,
        "duration": 3.12
    }
]